nt/uploads/2013/12/Roberto-Campanella-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Roberto Campanella" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Roberto Campanella"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/roberto-campanella/">View all articles by Roberto Campanella</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/07/intervista-al-regista-andrea-cigni/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Intervista al regista Andrea Cigni</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/07/gioacchino-rossini-1792-1868-semiramide/" rel="next">Gioachino Rossini (1792 &#8211; 1868): &#8220;Semiramide&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2015/07/venezia-teatro-la-fenice-juditha-triumphans/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</s